    "Training involves changing the weights of the model.",
    "Weights determine how it interprets and generates text.",
    "Their number is usually in the billions.",
    "Weights form the parameters that encode the model's understanding of language and its knowledge about the world.",
    "Note that training a model is something most users will never do themselves."
